children.text: Ibotta is the free app that saves you cash on things you buy every day. It’s simple to use whether you’re buying groceries, shopping, dining out, or even using your favorite apps. There’s no need to hunt for promo codes, clip coupons, or leave money on the table with Ibotta at your side.Ibotta (I-bought-a) is your shopping sidekick, always there to help you get cash back on the brands you love. We’ve help our users save over $100,000,000; join today to get your slice of the action!START WITH THE IBOTTA APP:1. Unlock Savings - Unlock cash back rebates in the app before you shop2. Go Shopping - Buy the things you love from favorite stores, retailers, restaurants, and apps3. Verify Purchase & Get Cash - Submit your receipt or link your loyalty card and get cash backWith hundreds of dollars in exclusive savings and discounts, no app gets you more money back every time you shop. Ibotta lets shoppers use a single app to get cash back on purchases at more than 500,000 stores and restaurants including Walmart, Walgreens, Best Buy, and Applebee’s. And now, shoppers who launch from Ibotta can even earn cash on purchases from top apps like Groupon, Jet, Hotels.com, and Boxed.Ditch the coupons and go shopping to save on all things grocery, pharmacy, clothing, beauty, dining, electronics, mobile apps, and even your favorite beer, wine, and spirits. Simply get money back in your account on everyday purchases with the free Ibotta app. THE BEST SAVINGS AROUND• Over 750+ retailers available where you can shop in store & can earn; including Walmart, Target and Best Buy• Cash back on mobile app purchases; including Jet, Groupon, Drizly & Doordash• Hundreds of rebates each week, bundle deals available too• Promos & discounts for all of your favorite brands• Grocery, household, clothes, beauty, snacks, restaurants, alcohol, & more•Users have saved over $100,000,000!EARN EVEN MORE:• Invite Friends - Refer a friend and receive $5 each time a friend redeems their first rebate using your referral code.• Bonuses – Get extra cash rewards by buying featured products, redeeming items at specific retailers, or completing unique tasks. • Teamwork – Create teams with your friends and family to receive Teamwork Bonuses every month!Hit $20 & easily cash out via PayPal, Venmo or gift card! Like receiving money with Ibotta?Please take a moment to rate our app. Your feedback means the world to us –especially if that means more savings for everyone.Note: Ibotta may use your location to help find stores. Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
